    {
      "chapterUid": 71,
      "chapterTitle": "系辞下传",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300075287_71_16076-16385",
          "range": "16076-16288",
          "rangeStart": 16076,
          "rangeEnd": 16288,
          "markText": "君子藏器于身，待时而动，何不利之有？动而不括￼，是以出而有获，语成器而动者也",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
